                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7954" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0822</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1995 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蔚兰环保绿色创业抉择：个人理想与家族传统的平衡之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Weilan Environmental Protection&#39;s Green Entrepreneurial Decision: Balancing Personal Aspirations  with Family Traditions</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨晶，冯陈晨，文婷，蒋雨函，张婷宇，刘洋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆市蔚兰环保科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家族企业二代创业者；乡村振兴；乡村垃圾回收处理；绿色创业；机会-资源-动机（ORM）模型；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Second-generation entrepreneur in family business, Rural revitalization, Rural waste management, Green entrepreneurship, Opportunity-Resource-Motive (ORM) model.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例详述了家族企业第二代创业者廖子杰的绿色创业历程，他自海外归来后成立了蔚兰环保科技有限公司，并专注于乡村垃圾回收处理。在初始阶段，由于他的创业理念与父亲以及家族企业高层的观念存在差异，引发了剧烈的冲突和挑战。然而通过有效的沟通、技术创新以及市场拓展，他成功在乡村市场推出了一系列的垃圾无害化处理和资源化利用项目。至2023年，国家发布了一系列与农村生态保护相关的政策，进一步提高了乡村振兴和环境治理的重要性，同时，随着旅游业的复苏，廖子杰的初始努力显著提升了乡村的环境质量和旅游吸引力。尽管家族企业和父亲对廖子杰的努力有所认可，但是，蔚兰环保面临的竞争依然激烈，新的挑战也随之出现。面对这些问题，蔚兰环保如何进一步发展？本案例旨在帮助学生理解并运用“机会-资源-动机”（ORM）模型，深化对家族二代创业的复杂性的理解，并学习有效的创业策略与资源整合方式。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study depicts the green entrepreneurial process of Liao Zijie, the second-generation successor of a family business, who established the Weilan Environmental Protection Company after returning from overseas, focusing on rural waste management. In the initial phase, conflicts arose with his family business due to ideological differences. However, through effective communication, technological innovation, and market expansion, he successfully launched a series of projects in rural markets for harmless waste treatment and resource utilization. By 2023, with the revival of the tourism industry, Liao Zijie&#39;s early efforts significantly enhanced rural environmental quality and tourism appeal. Subsequently, the state issued a series of policies related to rural ecological protection, further elevating the importance of rural revitalization and environmental governance. While Liao&#39;s efforts have been acknowledged by his family business and his father, Weilan Environmental Protection is still facing fierce competition and emerging challenges. In the face of these issues, how will Weilan Environmental Protection further develop? This case study, through an in-depth exploration of Liao Zijie&#39;s entrepreneurial process, aims to help students understand and apply the &quot;Opportunity-Resource-Motive&quot; (ORM) model, deepen their understanding of the complexities of second-generation entrepreneurship in family businesses, and learn effective entrepreneurial strategies and resource integration methods.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；绿色创业；机会-资源-动机模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
